    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You've gotta see this beauty \u2013 it\u2019s honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've taken such good care of it that it\u2019s still in absolute mint condition, inside and out. It drives like a dream and looks even better in person. If you're looking for something that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is the one! Shoot me a message if you want to come by and take a look; I\u2019d love to show it to you! \u2728",
      "price": 44900.0,
