      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Presenting a true automotive masterpiece in showroom condition. This vehicle has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage, preserving its original luster and pristine factory finish. The exterior is flawless, free of any chips or imperfections, while the interior still carries that fresh, new-car scent with leather that feels supple and untouched. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, boasting a comprehensive service history and performance that mirrors the day it rolled off the assembly line. Every button, sensor, and feature functions perfectly. This is not just a used car; it is a collector-grade example for the most discerning enthusiast who demands perfection.",
